Sazka AS Postpones Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, CTK Says

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-07-19T10:49:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/sazka-as-postpones-extraordinary-shareholders-meeting-ctk-says.html
Lottery operator Sazka AS postponed
an extraordinary  shareholders’ meeting  from today to Aug. 22 for
procedural reasons,  CTK  reported, citing Zdenek Ertl, head of
the Association of the Sport Federation of the  Czech Republic , a
minority shareholder,  Sazka’s largest shareholder, the Czech Sports Association,
planned to call for the dismissal of former Chief Executive
Officer Ales Husak from the board of directors during the
meeting today, CTK added.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  